Package com.niklasarndt.healthchecksio

Class OkHttpResponseFuture

java.lang.Object
com.niklasarndt.healthchecksio.OkHttpResponseFuture
All Implemented Interfaces:
okhttp3.Callback
public class OkHttpResponseFuture
extends java.lang.Object
implements okhttp3.Callback

This class wraps a CompletableFuture object inside a OkHttp callback. For internal use only, you don't need to think too much about this one.


With much inspiration from stackoverflow.
